  "problem_spec": {
    "summary": "Use the unique positive even L^2 ground state of u''+u^{2n+1}=u to define A_n=∫u_n^2, extract the constant L = lim (n(A_n-1)-ln(n+1)) via Gamma/digamma asymptotics, apply Φ=floor(e^L), then compute a binomial-square expression modulo 1000.\n",
