        "type": "integer",
        "role": "given",
        "dependency": "independent"
      },
      {
        "name": "u_n",
        "type": "function",
        "role": "aux",
        "dependency": "dependent"
      },
      {
        "name": "A_n",
        "type": "real",
        "role": "aux",
        "dependency": "dependent"
      },
      {
        "name": "L",
        "type": "real",
        "role": "aux",
        "dependency": "dependent"
      },
      {
        "name": "Phi",
        "type": "integer",
        "role": "aux",
        "dependency": "dependent"
      },
      {
        "name": "R",
        "type": "integer",
        "role": "output",
        "dependency": "dependent"
      }
    ],
    "givens": [
      "For each integer n>=1, u_n is the unique u\\inC^2(R) with u>0, u even, u,u'\\inL^2(R), satisfying u''+u^{2n+1}=u.",
      "Define A_n = ∫_{R} u_n(t)^2 dt.",
      "Define L = lim_{n->∞} ( n(A_n-1) - ln(n+1) ).",
      "Define Phi = floor(e^L).",
      "Define R = (Σ_{j=0}^6 binom(6,j) Phi^j)^2 + 41 Phi, and reduce R modulo 1000."
    ],
    "ask": [
      "Compute R mod 1000."
    ]
  },
  "answer_spec": {
